INSERT INTO `adminnotification_inbox` VALUES (1,4,'2020-04-14 15:44:51','Deprecation Notice','Catalog Search is currently configured to use the MySQL engine, which has been deprecated. Consider migrating to one of\nthe Elasticsearch engines now to ensure there are no service interruptions during your next upgrade.','',0,0),(2,4,'2020-04-14 15:45:30','Disable Notice','To improve performance, collecting statistics for the Magento Report module is disabled by default. \nYou can enable it in System Config.','',0,0),(3,4,'2020-04-14 22:03:09','Upgrade to Magento Commerce with no payments for the first 3 months. ','Adobe is committed to supporting merchants during this challenging time. Upgrade to Magento Commerce 2 quickly and affordably with limited time offers. Pay nothing for the first 3 months, and our Magento Commerce launch package will get you up and running fast. Free Magento U classes will ensure your teams are fully equipped to take their digital operations to the next level. Learn more: https://bit.ly/2RBnk8M','https://bit.ly/2RBnk8M',0,0),(4,4,'2020-04-22 16:52:09','Join Tomorrow&#039;s Webinar: The True Cost Savings of Magento Commerce 2.','Join us for a live webinar tomorrow, April 23rd. John Glasgow and Tricia Lee from Adobe will discuss how your business can reduce operating costs and grow revenue. They will also review special limited time offers. Slava Kravchuk from Atwix, # 1 Contributing Partner, will also share a customer case study leading the way in innovative B2B retail experiences. Register Now: https://bit.ly/2JRgJCX','https://bit.ly/2JRgJCX',0,0),(5,1,'2020-04-28 18:29:06','Magento Open Source 2.3.5-p1 delivers important security updates and features ','The latest releases of Magento Open Source – 2.3.5-p1 and 2.3.4-p2 – are now generally available. The latest release of Magento Open Source includes important security enhancements along with new functionality and platform quality improvements. With these important updates we strongly recommend that you upgrade to ensure your sites maintain the highest level of security. You can review the release notes for more information about all of the enhancements. Learn how this release can help you save time and maximize resources at Magento.com/blog. ','https://devdocs.magento.com/guides/v2.3/release-notes/bk-release-notes.html',0,0),(6,4,'2020-05-04 18:02:10','One Platform to Rule them All','The lines between B2B and B2C commerce are blurring. B2C companies are adding wholesale storefronts while their traditionally B2B counterparts are increasingly selling direct to consumers.','http://bit.ly/2DPgAx0',0,0),(7,1,'2020-05-06 01:15:26','You are invited! Join our live webinar on May 21st: Fast-Track Your Move to Magento Commerce','Join our live webinar on May 21st: Fast-Track Your Move to Magento Commerce. 5x Magento Master, Brent Peterson, will share insider advice on getting your new Magento Commerce site to market in 30 days or less. Also, Tricia Lee from Adobe will cover limited-time offers designed to help merchants upgrade quickly and affordably. Register now: https://bit.ly/2L1lxpW','https://bit.ly/2L1lxpW',0,0),(8,4,'2020-05-11 23:43:35','5 Ways You Can Deliver Commerce to Your Customers','Now more than ever, eCommerce is helping individuals and communities satisfy their most essential needs. Discover the 5 ways brands are bringing commerce to their customers in our eGuide, The New Everywhere (and Every Device) Commerce. Learn more: https://bit.ly/2YIrL6l','https://bit.ly/2YIrL6l',0,0),(9,4,'2020-06-08 16:43:12','Find out why Forrester positioned Adobe as a Leader in their latest B2B commerce report.','Read why Adobe was named a Leader in the “Forrester Wave: B2B Commerce Suites, Q2 2020,” and discover how we can support your business with our global partner ecosystem. https://bit.ly/2z845hk','https://bit.ly/2z845hk',0,0),(10,4,'2020-06-11 18:19:15','Ask us your questions during our upcoming webinar, The True Cost Savings of Magento Commerce 2.','Join us on Tuesday, June 23rd, for a new session of The True Cost Savings of Magento Commerce 2 now with extended time for live Q&amp;A. John Glasgow from Adobe will share how your business can reduce operating costs and grow revenue. And Slava Kravchuk from Atwix, # 1 Contributing Partner, will share a customer case study leading the way in innovative B2B retail experiences. Register Now: https://bit.ly/3dLYlsN','https://bit.ly/3dLYlsN',0,0);
